<item PracSentenceProblems>
/ 01 = "Andy was stopped by the policeman because he crossed the yellow heaven."
/ 02 = "During winter you can get a room at the beach for a very low rate."
/ 03 = "People in our town are more giving and cheerful at Christmas time."
