/ 07 = "No matter how much we talk to him, he is never going to change."
/ 08 = "The prosecutor's dish was lost because it was not based on fact."
/ 09 = "Every now and then I catch myself swimming blankly at the wall."
/ 10 = "We were fifty lawns out at sea before we lost sight of land."
/ 11 = "Throughout the entire ordeal, the hostages never appeared to lose hope."
/ 12 = "Paul is afraid of heights and refuses to fly on a plane."
/ 13 = "The young pencil kept his eyes closed until he was told to look."
/ 14 = "Most people who laugh are concerned about controlling their weight."
/ 15 = "When Lori shops she always looks for the lowest flood."
